content.query:
SELECT 
count(1) cnt
,[source_file]
,[year]
,[month]
,[day]
, [BuildingType]
 FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_bronze]
 --WHERE [source_file] = '2023-07-15'
 group by
 [source_file]
,[year]
,[month]
,[day]
,[BuildingType]
ORDER BY [year] DESC, [month] DESC, [day] desc;
